title: VA Easy Pop - Wild Places (Dutch Treat ^A144 VBR MP3)
description:
Modern varied music for a sunny terrace (so I imagine). Butterflies, songs brought by the wind. Detected by my alarm system and stored in a queue (until its full).

Very different, hard to combine. Music that gives you energy (see also A143) instead of drawing the attention to itself... Enjoy,
